ent-ActionAbominationAssimilate = Assimilate
    .desc = Begin assimilating an incapacitated humanoid. They will become a mimic too.

ent-ActionAbominationChooseStructure = Choose Flesh Structure
    .desc = Pick which structure you'll secrete with the Secrete Flesh action.

ent-ActionAbominationGruntAcidSpray = Acid Spray
    .desc = Vomit a cone of corrosive acid in the target direction.

ent-ActionAbominationGruntCharge = Charge
    .desc = Wind up and barrel forward, smashing through anything in your path.

ent-ActionAbominationGruntSlam = Slam
    .desc = Leap to a position and slam down, knocking enemies prone.

ent-ActionAbominationGruntSpit = Acid Spit
    .desc = Hawk up a glob of corrosive acid at the target.

ent-ActionAbominationMimicRevert = Drop Disguise
    .desc = Burst out of your current form and return to your combat shape.

ent-ActionAbominationMimicTransform = Mimic
    .desc = Take the shape of one of your assimilated victims for a limited time.

ent-ActionAbominationPlantKudzu = Spread Kudzu
    .desc = Vomit out a fast-spreading kudzu source under yourself.

ent-ActionAbominationSecreteStructure = Secrete Flesh
    .desc = Secrete the chosen flesh structure on the targeted tile.

ent-ActionAbominationSpiderLeap = Pounce
    .desc = Pounce onto a target, knocking them down briefly.

ent-ActionAbominationSpiderSpit = Acid Spit
    .desc = Spit a glob of acid at a target.
